{"tid":1339801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗白衣人血洗西鐵站　《蘋果》記者被毆","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:46:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":100,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"d3600cefe59e02b5268f37e0a5cef0abefa27df8","tid":1339801,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563722577_0290.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563722577_0290.png&h=b2bf6c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數十名白衣人衝入車廂，見人就打，血洗元朗西鐵站。立場新聞圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563722872_7190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563722872_7190.jpg&h=ec0f0bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563722874_1df3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563722874_1df3.jpg&h=d806da2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563722872_ba19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563722872_ba19.jpg&h=f86545e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入夜後，大批白衣人在元朗西鐵站內聚集，其間不斷起哄，又揮舞藤條及木棍毆打途人，其間立法會議員林卓庭亦在場直播情況，但遭數十名白衣人圍毆至嘴角流血。<br />\n<br />\n白衣人其後更衝入月台，見人就打，有乘客更跪在地上求饒，《蘋果》記者更被多名白衣人打傷，情況嚴重。"},{"pid":"cdb959f3863ca80ed84bf0d5870d86559aa5b973","tid":1339801,"uid":20933,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563722872_3ff3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563722872_3ff3.jpg&h=247a6c0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"908b20554e53811469b1bd7c9e991d39531b2c42","tid":1339801,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190721/59848364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190721%2F59848364&d=gWuinA8KpjkBZIRqFxHaGgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=84e82f36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190721%2F59848364&h=a830eccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190721/59848364</a>"},{"pid":"40f6d5a86ac6118b957821ef41cd6020e3cf4b99","tid":1339801,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c3a710b24e962340242eea58a05ed66e72a39414","tid":1339801,"uid":46314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"988cf2ad285aaecd5c916ae2af8396abd3503a03","tid":1339801,"uid":141505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"班老黑走撚晒先黎 屌你老母"},{"pid":"d8ce7f1a7ef2fc11a6066c3ff6bbdeca3ea823db","tid":1339801,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推<br />\n<br />\n屌佢地老母</span>"},{"pid":"069f117c86530e95e52aec10d9f135cb0f6cca92","tid":1339801,"uid":29093,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推上國際新聞<br />\n<br />\n立場記者 同 另一個記者都被人襲擊, 其中一人受重傷<br />\n立場記者依家負傷做緊直播 ...<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線 .....</span>"},{"pid":"e7ef2f92c5a7cff50059abf47d15fc998c13b277","tid":1339801,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cdb959f3863ca